    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure is straightforward, involving basic SQL operations such as SELECT statements, variable assignments, and conditional checks. It does not involve complex logic, loops, or advanced SQL features, making it relatively easy to understand and maintain."
        }
      ]
    },
